### Record Payment
POST http://localhost:3000/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "clientId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
  "amount": 50000,
  "paymentMethod": "MPESA",
  "paymentDate": "2024-12-14",
  "referenceNumber": "QH12345678",
  "notes": "December payment"
}

### Get Payment by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/payments/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List All Payments
GET http://localhost:3000/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List Payments with Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/payments?clientId={{clientId}}&paymentMethod=MPESA&startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Payments by Client
GET http://localhost:3000/payments/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
